          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It is not 100 percent clear that Cuomo is going to sign the bill, but he’s under pressure — and he’s already suggesting he understands the imperative for the legislation. So that’s a good sign — and certainly a sign that our reporting made a big impact.",
